{"tid":2192612,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【無圖】童顏巨乳直播主「湘湘」透視爆乳上衣誘惑　不規則「雪乳亂晃」讓人忍不住暈船","createTime":"2020-09-07T08:38:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T14:47:42.000Z","uid":217211,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"82a2555e0c96cf127e7dcbe3f26f71fd51bb8b39","tid":2192612,"uid":217211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.mymypic.net/data/attachment/forum/202008/20/103827wjjozl6jh7zvoifk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymypic.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202008%2F20%2F103827wjjozl6jh7zvoifk.jpg&h=97644da7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n越來越多優質妹子加入遊戲直播行列，今天這位童顏巨乳直播主「湘湘」就是近日鄉民口中討論度很高的妹子，標準童顏巨乳外型的他，可愛臉蛋配上不科學的飽滿雪乳，讓她的一舉一動都備受粉絲關注。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mymypic.net/data/attachment/forum/202008/20/103828e1t0aupc1olp11uc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymypic.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202008%2F20%2F103828e1t0aupc1olp11uc.jpg&h=d344033c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mymypic.net/data/attachment/forum/202008/20/103828dduqnlddh4fmdem9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymypic.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202008%2F20%2F103828dduqnlddh4fmdem9.jpg&h=f1052ab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mymypic.net/data/attachment/forum/202008/20/103827q04ih81ikbwm8v0i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymypic.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202008%2F20%2F103827q04ih81ikbwm8v0i.jpg&h=dbf9b2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mymypic.net/data/attachment/forum/202008/20/10382995aazecc395m0l5c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymypic.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202008%2F20%2F10382995aazecc395m0l5c.jpg&h=97cf22a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mymypic.net/data/attachment/forum/202008/20/103829svppc6zcpzc11rei.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymypic.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202008%2F20%2F103829svppc6zcpzc11rei.jpg&h=75f66189&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mymypic.net/data/attachment/forum/202008/20/103830xo171lr31nl8gprz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymypic.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202008%2F20%2F103830xo171lr31nl8gprz.jpg&h=d7a28fdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mymypic.net/data/attachment/forum/202008/20/1038306b4mzt7lzlotr94w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymypic.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202008%2F20%2F1038306b4mzt7lzlotr94w.jpg&h=05ce5d40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mymypic.net/data/attachment/forum/202008/20/103830h0vifv27b75eag2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymypic.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202008%2F20%2F103830h0vifv27b75eag2e.jpg&h=f5aab399&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mymypic.net/data/attachment/forum/202008/20/103831wzh2h1yv4ayyf46w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymypic.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202008%2F20%2F103831wzh2h1yv4ayyf46w.jpg&h=c326c469&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目前是人氣直播主，同時也是網路上知名網美的湘湘，女神般完美形象也讓她受到不少廠商青睞，常常能在她粉專上看到她替各式各樣產品代言，邀約接到手軟！不知為何，每次看著湘湘代言宅味十足的電競產品，感覺都香到不行，果然東西還是要看人穿看人用。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mymypic.net/data/attachment/forum/202008/20/103831bc6ldvcbdftbbp6p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymypic.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202008%2F20%2F103831bc6ldvcbdftbbp6p.jpg&h=ae55f67b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mymypic.net/data/attachment/forum/202008/20/103831si8semx9bqm00rxm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymypic.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202008%2F20%2F103831si8semx9bqm00rxm.jpg&h=cf80010f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.mymypic.net/data/attachment/forum/202008/20/103832u8bf3elxk8uoxxlz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymypic.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202008%2F20%2F103832u8bf3elxk8uoxxlz.jpg&h=4ebfbceb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.mymypic.net/data/attachment/forum/202008/20/103832rzvdn9ndax28idy2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymypic.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202008%2F20%2F103832rzvdn9ndax28idy2.jpg&h=db2acbbb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.mymypic.net/data/attachment/forum/202008/20/103832o64mo666p9pxzbj8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymypic.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202008%2F20%2F103832o64mo666p9pxzbj8.jpg&h=b68279c8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.mymypic.net/data/attachment/forum/202008/20/103833rf8z88z5av1a2d5r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymypic.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202008%2F20%2F103833rf8z88z5av1a2d5r.jpg&h=7b814c04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n常常穿著透視爆乳上衣直播的湘湘，每次她這麼穿，胸前曲線都若隱若現，時而挺胸、時而前傾的模樣，更是讓她渾圓雪乳不規則上下亂晃，讓人看如癡如醉，不知不覺抖內到抖信用卡公司打來啊～"},{"pid":"10eece714e302b304f0b61529c96c815e08eba16","tid":2192612,"uid":217211,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:38:48.000Z","msg":"呢個真係好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b736fba2caf21962be0a9f6af8b7e0ac10f9a994","tid":2192612,"uid":3994,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:40:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JTVNd2Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJTVNd2Y.jpg&h=cad9ade3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8035dbfd6706e5a3a7f46c2a0c905d9e3a222740","tid":2192612,"uid":47764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:41:21.000Z","msg":"比toyz屌過 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9